# Session 012 – Conversation

## Goal

Define the Conversation concept.

---

## Decisions

Conversations are a core mechanism for learning rather than a traditional chatbot.

Every Conversation has a clear purpose.

Five Conversation types were defined:

- Discover
- Reflect
- Clarify
- Celebrate
- Coach

DailyPaws remembers previous conversations and naturally builds upon them.

Conversations contribute to the understanding of the Dog, Relationships and future Insights.

